The paper discusses the design and implementation of a specialized integrated circuit for deep neural network learning and inference acceleration. This falls under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), electronic devices and circuits (cs.ET), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
